  "detailed_description": "Ride day and night, taking on risky jobs for the Road Baron, avoiding traffic and other bikers on endless dangerous roads, all of that while you blast some original punk rock music!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346500/extras/3ca8d9a615d99debf0876fd1bc35a0d0.poster.avif?t=1762272899\" width=612 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346500/extras/3ca8d9a615d99debf0876fd1bc35a0d0.webm?t=1762272899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346500/extras/3ca8d9a615d99debf0876fd1bc35a0d0.mp4?t=1762272899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>In Road Scars: Origins you play as Adam, an aspiring motorcyclist, fighting to join the Road Slicers, the biggest motorcycle club on the town. Do you have what it takes to reach your goal?<br></li><li>A fusion of classic games such as Road Rash and Road Fighter.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346500/extras/738daea738d12684b5eede4737860636.poster.avif?t=1762272899\" width=612 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346500/extras/738daea738d12684b5eede4737860636.webm?t=1762272899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346500/extras/738daea738d12684b5eede4737860636.mp4?t=1762272899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play one of the 3 game modes (or all of them):<br></li><li>On the story mode, take on challenges and racings and follow Adam's jorney.<br></li><li>On the arcade mode, get the best possible score and try to reach the top of the Steam Leaderboards.<br></li><li>On the challenge mode, unlock achievements throught 48 challenges and racings.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346500/extras/ab3ab649b9a0c46ce806ae1e4235bac6.poster.avif?t=1762272899\" width=612 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346500/extras/ab3ab649b9a0c46ce806ae1e4235bac6.webm?t=1762272899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346500/extras/ab3ab649b9a0c46ce806ae1e4235bac6.mp4?t=1762272899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Avoid traffic and knock down enemies through procedurally generated roads.<br></li><li>Retro visuals and cutscenes with comicbook style.<br></li><li>Story mode with about 1 hour gameplay.<br></li><li>Endless arcade mode<br></li><li>48 challenges<br></li><li>Day-nigh dinamyc system<br></li><li>Original punk rock soundtrack with 6 musics</li></ul>",
